data.description: Welcome to the newly remodeled 232 Haywicke Place in the established Staffordshire pool community in Wake Forest. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is located at the end of a quiet cul de sac, making the back yard large and private and traffic non-existent.  Home has a generous 2 car garage with additional storage built in. Formal dining room and living room with built in bookshelves, family room, and large bedrooms. Large back deck, walk-in crawlspace, gas fireplace. Home has new LVP flooring, carpet, HVAC, new paint, several windows, appliances, granite counter tops in kitchen, new bath room cabinets, new walk in primary shower. Refrigerator conveys. Convenient to shopping, dining, the Wake Forest bus loop, Wake Forest High School, walking trails, and the SE Baptist Seminary. Welcome home!!!
